node.text: During this pandemic, @lafamilyhousing has tripled their shelter beds in an effort to get as many people off the streets as possible. These hygiene kits are given to people that enter the shelters. If you are local, please consider donating these items which can be picked up by their volunteers. Donate at the link in bio! Thank you!
